name: Transmission
comments: From the first of two Peel Sessions by Joy Division, recorded on January 31, 1979 and broadcast on February 14. The version released as a single (FAC 13) was recorded in July 1979. An earlier recording of "Transmission" was made in May 1978 for a proposed album for RCA that in the end was not released. The RCA recordings including "Transmission" have been available on unofficial and semi-official releases for many years and some of them, but not "Transmission", were included on the official Heart and Soul box set in 1997. As far as the editors are aware, the RCA recording of "Transmission" has not had a full official release.
